    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has plenty of life left for its next adventure! I\u2019ve taken great care of it, so it runs smoothly and looks great too. If you're looking for a reliable car that\u2019s ready to hit the road today, this is the one. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a good home!",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
